title: A.V. Club Live: Joel Hodgson explains the “kabuki” of the new Mystery Science Theater 3000
text:
By Erik Adams @ErikMAdams Feb 22, 2017 4:03 PM 
It’s not just the voices of Crow T. Robot and Tom Servo that have changed—there’s a whole new method to puppeteering on display in the 11th season of Mystery Science Theater 3000.
